===Etymology===
From {{etyl|xno|en}} {{term|mortgage|lang=fro}}, {{etyl|frm|en}} {{term|mortgage|lang=frm}}, from {{etyl|fro|en}} {{term|mort gage||death pledge|lang=fro}}, after a translation of judicial {{etyl|ML.|en}} {{term|mortuum vadium|lang=la}} or ''mortuum wadium'', from {{term|mortuum|lang=la}} + ''vadium'' or ''wadium'', of {{etyl|gem|en}} ({{etyl|frk|en}}) origin, from a root *''waddi'', ''wadja''. Cf. ''[[gage]]'' and also ''[[wage]]''.

